{"tid":1033830,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】中國承諾再買1000萬噸美大豆　官媒：利益度量的結果","createTime":"2019-02-23T12:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:51:01.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"463b73f7b200dabcc1ec84f9a41b4cf0b66737da","tid":1033830,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2476179/org/2a7bda8ff98f48ded0caa66771c58e59.jpg/iQg0DVXUzlcNluCwrTWBZq08ATAx2XytUCZ2RlAmdkY?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2476179%2Forg%2F2a7bda8ff98f48ded0caa66771c58e59.jpg%2FiQg0DVXUzlcNluCwrTWBZq08ATAx2XytUCZ2RlAmdkY%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=3873bfbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美高層官員周四（21日）於華盛頓舉行為期2日的貿易談判，美國農業部長索尼&middot;珀杜（Sonny Perdue）在Twitter帳號發文稱，中國承諾購買額外1000萬噸美國大豆。此前，中美上月30日至31日在華盛頓舉行貿易談判期間，中方已承諾會購買多500萬噸美國大豆。<br />\n<br />\n對此，有聲音質疑中方對美方的讓步太多。國務院主辦的中央直屬黨報《經濟日報》旗下微博「陶然筆記」則發文稱，用大豆來表明立場或釋放善意，都是利益度量的結果。在進口大豆問題上，要看清三大因素：中國的需求，美國的需求以及中美間的利益重合點。<br />\n<br />\n「陶然筆記」文章指出，從中國需求來說，大豆市場缺口非常大。據資料顯示，中國一年有9000多萬噸（約90%）的大豆要從國際市場進口，主要用於榨油和飼料加工。文章分析稱，去年中美貿易戰爆發，中國大豆進口量減少了7.9%，主要就是美國大豆的進口量下降。惟中國減少對美國大豆的需求，目前尚不能完全找到替代對象來補足缺口。<br />\n<br />\n「陶然筆記」繼續指出，美國作為世界第一大大豆生產國，一年能生產1億噸左右的大豆，但其國內市場無法消耗，差不多一半左右的大豆依賴出口。去年特朗普挑起貿易戰後，遭到中國的堅決反擊，美國豆農首當其衝。<br />\n<br />\n結合中美對大豆進出口的需求，文章稱，從中美間的利益重合點來說，不同的資源稟賦決定了中美農產品貿易具有很強的互補性。這意味著美國需要中國，中國也需要美國。而這種「需要」變成談價的條件之餘，也應以形成利益共識為目標。中國購買美國大豆，除了增加跟美國豆農利益共識，也為中國農業結構調整騰出時間和空間。"},{"pid":"723bb9e5799aa0b0d1b471b076dbedd3dbae16f3","tid":1033830,"uid":51346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"劍指28000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001fd2e86783a7053df1801df8283d8f78a30586","tid":1033830,"uid":98887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"Per day"},{"pid":"b45faba7fb1eae51fb6c29d33af8484aee393988","tid":1033830,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"千升"},{"pid":"4bb31801c521bdaff740e6bbf7d383b3808a4390","tid":1033830,"uid":165782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"要咁多大豆整豆漿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d0ee781637e414f9545c6a5b1a7e5b669e216e","tid":1033830,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:52:04.000Z","msg":"每日定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01cd5a941555c42b2fe3b6af3d8469808f3867a","tid":1033830,"uid":27882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"講撚到驚美國啲大豆冇人要,俾面你求其買小小幫襯下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27dd8e57d0a5b5ebade81f131af645e3bda4771","tid":1033830,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"香港過萬億<br />\n怕咩"},{"pid":"668e08a79e414cb891c78fa35371c820e4ca21ff","tid":1033830,"uid":221051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"傾黎傾去都淨係買豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a3b29445272c68dd38dbb9d26fb438c78a35c1","tid":1033830,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPeA25h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPeA25h.png&h=02922393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0958d2547a741f290d0e413e55a13c4fe2766a0b","tid":1033830,"uid":37490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3b29445272c68dd38dbb9d26fb438c78a35c1","tid":1033830,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPeA25h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPeA25h.png&h=029223